Telkom has announced new FreeMe Promo All-Network voice bundles. The bundles are available for post-paid and top-up customers on FreeMe and FreeMe Family. They are billed per second and are valid for 31 days. Telkom said that the bundles can be used to call any mobile network within South Africa and can be purchased as once-off or recurring bundles. It added that the bundles will be exclusively available to FreeMe and FreeMe Family customers from 5 July 2018. You can find the full list of bundles and pricing details below. Read: Telkom appoints new chief financial officer